          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "二皇儿含悲泪一旁站定，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "孤又惭孤又悔孤又伤心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "主公，近日病体如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉，悔不听先生之言，有此大败，损兵折将，乃孤王之罪矣！"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "军家胜败，古之常理，主公保重要紧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "马谡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是啊，主公保重要紧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，参谋言得极是，宫外伺候。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马谡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马谡下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，先生，"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "主公。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看马谡，人才如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "幼常虽然年幼，颇有才能，乃国家栋梁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不然哪，不然！孤看马谡，言过其实，终无大用；若为重任，他必有所失。先"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "生，你要牢牢紧记！"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二皇儿，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘永、刘理",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "父皇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "朕亡后，军国大事，全仗先生。汝弟兄，侍先生要侍之若父。向前去，拜过你"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相父！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘永、刘理",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同二黄散板） 走上前来忙跪定，"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "搀起刘氏后代根。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四弟在哪里？四弟……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵云上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "主公！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四弟……"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "一把手拉住了子龙手，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "我和你患难相从共死生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "我死后全仗你照应他们。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "长坂坡曾救过阿斗小命"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "主公！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "长坂坡曾救过阿斗小命"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "主公但把心放定，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "保孤之事我担承！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "霎时间腹内痛心血上涌"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘备吐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮、赵云、刘永、刘理",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "保重了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "两弟仇东吴恨化了灰尘！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘备死，诸葛亮、赵云、刘永、刘理同哭。）"
        }
      ],
